title: My 15 Scans - May 2016 (gnv64)
description:

I am an amateur book maker. Its my endevour to scan & convert old printed books & magazines to reasonably good quality PDFs as they are not available in digital format. I have made 500+ PDFs over past 6 years. I have digitized almost 75% of my personal library. Here I am sharing some recent scans. Kindly comment on the PDF quality after reading.
